11:25.660 --> 11:27.370
Well, it has its uses.

11:27.370 --> 11:29.440
You just can't expect
one number to tell you

11:29.440 --> 11:32.380
the truth about our
gargantuan global economy.

11:32.380 --> 11:37.040
Despite what the media says,
it's just not that simple.

11:37.040 --> 11:38.580
I can't believe you, Cray.

11:38.580 --> 11:40.990
