backwood extrusion press,

11:50.280 --> 11:51.570
I can learn a little economics.

11:51.570 --> 11:54.000
Maybe it'll even help me
figure out when my old factory

11:54.000 --> 11:55.110
job is coming back.

11:55.110 --> 11:56.680
Uh, about that.

11:56.680 --> 11:59.710
Hey Mr. Magic Man, why
don't you let me show

11:59.710 --> 12:02.330
you why they call me Cray Cray!

12:02.330 --> 12:03.770
You know what, I'll
tell you in a second.

12:03.770 --> 12:05.110
